### Risk

**Medium.** If the early return is accidentally removed or its condition changed,
every internal redirect would double-count downstream stats (`downstream_rq_completed_`,
`downstream_rq_2xx_`, etc.), silently corrupting metrics, dashboards, and any
auto-scaling or alerting rules that depend on request counts.

