## Gap 5 — `encodeHeaders` header-validator `new_headers` swap branch (`conn_manager_impl.cc:2014–2023`)

### Code under scrutiny

```cpp
// conn_manager_impl.cc:2014-2023  (inside ActiveStream::encodeHeaders)
